# Cloudflare Workers static-assets headers (host of record since 2026-07-17).
# Mirrors the 5 defense-in-depth headers nginx.conf serves on the Railway
# fallback (SECURITY_AUDIT.md § M3-M6) — without this file the CF deploy
# ships none of them.
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=()
